Class UserParameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • toolkit.domain.UserParameters

  • public class UserParameters
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by James Euesden on 09/03/2016. Used by the Controller and View to contain the users data about what they wish to inspect and any additional parameters for that initial data.
